The Wife of the President, Mrs. Aisha Buhari is visiting Bauchi state today. The visit is part of her campaign to canvass votes for her husband, President Muhammadu Buhari, in his re-election bid in the 2019 general elections. She is expected to hold a town-hall meeting with women groups in the state. Our reporter said Mrs. Buhari was however represented by wife of the Vice President, Mrs Dolapo‎ Osinbajo.  Details later… Aisha Buhari condoles Goje’s family Aisha Buhari condoles Goje over wife’s death Aisha Buhari: I’m using 2015 election campaign cars